00:20:26,520 --> 00:20:32,580
Fuline, if General asks about me, just say I am out for shopping, can you?

230
00:20:32,580 --> 00:20:34,460
Fuline understands.

231
00:20:42,340 --> 00:20:44,060
You are here.

232
00:20:49,730 --> 00:20:52,010
What you call me for?

233
00:20:52,880 --> 00:20:57,110
Did you find out what's the crown prince's heirloom that Xiao Hansheng has?

234
00:20:57,110 --> 00:20:59,320
I promised to remain in the General's Manor in your behalf.

235
00:20:59,320 --> 00:21:02,230
But I didn't agree to do thing requested by you.

236
00:21:04,130 --> 00:21:07,170
But I did thing for you.

237
00:21:20,930 --> 00:21:22,920
Xiaoqian.

238
00:21:22,920 --> 00:21:25,320
She's a close acquaintance of the Grand Chancellor.

239
00:21:25,320 --> 00:21:27,570
She'll be a threat if she remains by your side.

240
00:21:27,570 --> 00:21:29,590
You're insane.

241
00:21:29,590 --> 00:21:32,070
I'm insane?

242
00:21:32,910 --> 00:21:35,060
On the night of your marriage with Xiao Hansheng,

243
00:21:35,060 --> 00:21:38,270
she helped my foolish elder brother plot your demise.

244
00:21:38,270 --> 00:21:40,400
Indeed I help you.

245
00:21:40,400 --> 00:21:44,310
I can't let such a traitorous servant live.

246
00:21:47,980 --> 00:21:50,500
I will not do anything for you again.

247
00:21:50,500 --> 00:21:53,520
What's going to your pitiful elder sister?

248
00:21:53,520 --> 00:21:55,290
If she hasn't my medicine.

249
00:21:55,290 --> 00:21:59,080
she won't even survive tonight.

250
00:22:01,150 --> 00:22:05,730
My marriage is a simple affair. Your Highness doesn't need to offer such lavish gifts.

251
00:22:05,730 --> 00:22:08,650
General Xiao, you're a Fuyuan General personally appointed by His Majesty.

252
00:22:08,650 --> 00:22:13,090
The Xiao family has contributed greatly to defending the country and are people I respect deeply.

253
00:22:13,090 --> 00:22:17,380
You are of a similar age as I am. We should get along like brothers.

254
00:22:17,380 --> 00:22:22,470
However, I never had the chance to speak with you.

255
00:22:23,150 --> 00:22:27,710
I'm just a military general. I dare not see myself as equals with the imperial family.

256
00:22:27,710 --> 00:22:31,920
I can't accept such lavish gifts.

257
00:22:36,250 --> 00:22:38,040
General, you're being too severe.

258
00:22:38,040 --> 00:22:41,180
I should be the one looking up to you.

259
00:22:41,180 --> 00:22:43,900
If General, does not mind.

260
00:22:43,900 --> 00:22:47,460
Treat these as resources for the soldiers at the borders.

261
00:22:47,460 --> 00:22:49,370
What do you think?

262
00:22:52,020 --> 00:22:55,930
I thank you on behalf of the soldiers at the borders.

263
00:22:57,860 --> 00:23:01,010
Xiao Hansheng.

264
00:23:01,010 --> 00:23:04,900
One day, I'll make you serve me.

265
00:23:07,300 --> 00:23:09,220
I am sorry.

266
00:23:17,320 --> 00:23:19,140
Your Highness.

267
00:23:20,720 --> 00:23:23,170
Both of you, stand on guard.

268
00:23:30,160 --> 00:23:38,570
credit

269
