♫ <i>Endless love and hate remain</i> ♫
♫ <i>Harping on old grudges like the stars</i> ♫

271
00:23:51,390 --> 00:23:57,510
♫ <i>Taking a stroll with a few people</i> ♫
♫ <i>Age old yearning turns into wine</i> ♫

